After a lot of testing by Facebook and Instagram, the ability to hide the number of likes was officially launched in 2019, and has been rolling out in various countries. The feature offers the option to hide the number of likes from others as well as your own. Users get to hide the number of likes their posts receive from the public and choose whether they can see the number of likes for all posts in their feed. The company says it does this to “give people control over their experience” when using social media platforms. Here is how to: How to hide likes on Instagram To hide likes from a previous post, here’s what you need to do: How to hide likes on Facebook